<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Species Gallery | ACCC</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="logo">ACCC</div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="About.html">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="Species-index.html" class="active">Species</a></li>
                <li><a href="Contact.html">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section class="index-header">
            <h1>Atlantic Slope Species</h1>
            <p>Explore the diversity of freshwater bivalves found throughout our focus watersheds.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="gallery-grid">
            <a href="species/elliptio-complanata.html" class="species-card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="assets/images/elliptio-thumb.jpg" alt="Elliptio complanata">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3><i>Elliptio complanata</i></h3>
                    <p class="common-name">Eastern Elliptio</p>
                    <span class="status-tag secure">Secure</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="species-snas.html" class="species-card">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="assets/nasutus_reduced.jpg" alt="Sagittunio nasutus">
                </div>
                <div class="card-content">
                    <h3><i>Sagittunio nasutus</i></h3>
                    <p class="common-name">Eastern Pondmussel</p>
                    <span class="status-tag threatened">Threatened</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <div class="species-card placeholder">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <p>More species profiles coming soon...</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

</body>
</html>
